{"tid":2406071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"感情不重形式  情侶減拜年唔可惜「免見割席親友」","createTime":"2021-02-13T01:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T02:33:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29140a67e8b850b53fc8f2b6c640414468dd2e86","tid":2406071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/OMZMYJN2I5CZBFZNWVXFUHNIOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FOMZMYJN2I5CZBFZNWVXFUHNIOI%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=f7822c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FOMZMYJN2I5CZBFZNWVXFUHNIOI%2F&h=8677b6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/OMZMYJN2I5CZBFZNWVXFUHNIOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n感情不重形式 <br />\n情侶減拜年唔可惜「免見割席親友」<br />\n<br />\n【市民賀歲】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：50辣車放煙花狂飆 當警無到<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】農曆新年，港人均會按習俗互訪拜年。在疫情仍然反覆下，政府早前呼籲市民減少新春團拜。記者昨日隨機訪問外出港人，均表示難以完全捨棄傳統習俗，雖然會減少拜年次數，仍會到訪至親家中。不過在社會運動後，親友或因政見產生矛盾，有人笑言疫情反令他可乘機避免與已「割席」的親友碰頭 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HFbXVE0JgbReokt0cezuskvhbj4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYBCYUBNHRHMRHJITLSQNBEUIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHFbXVE0JgbReokt0cezuskvhbj4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYBCYUBNHRHMRHJITLSQNBEUIM.jpg&h=66e4a689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊先生： 「我唔想啲節日好似情緒勒索咁，一定要同一啲唔想見嘅人見面囉。」<br />\n<br />\n政府多次呼籲市民減少拜年，並。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民間「煙花滙」炮仗聲四起<br />\n<br />\n一家四口外出拜年的左先生表示，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s8qgb2P31xFxOj0MWBBnMLvf9lQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6ATQAGUM6BC45KKWSUIFFKKOYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs8qgb2P31xFxOj0MWBBnMLvf9lQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6ATQAGUM6BC45KKWSUIFFKKOYY.jpg&h=a7e79b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周小姐： 「（冇得拜年）唔可惜喎，一啲so called嘅團聚唔係話咁高質素咁真誠嘅交流。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份受訪者視像拜年<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。亦有受訪者表示，會改以視像交流形式拜年，認為是折衷辦法。<br />\n<br />\n在一片大失所望的嘆息聲中，亦有人視之為幸運。今年只會到父母家拜年的情侶周小姐及楊先生，均未為要減少與親友見面而感到可惜。周小姐明言以往的拜年質素不高，亦不真誠，「可能係同一啲唔係咁啱牙嘅親戚朋友夾硬見個面咁，係形式囉。但我覺得呢年之後，我哋唔係着重形式。」<br />\n<br />\n她續指，持續逾一年的疫潮反而令她不再單靠大時大節才與親友見面，變相會更珍惜每次與親友相聚的機會，交流更深入，「冇以前咁表面囉」，反而對維繫感情更有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n疫症亦成為避免跟政見不同的親友拜年的「免死金牌」。楊先生表示，過去兩年的社會氣氛，令他開始減少與「不必要的人」見面交流，「真㗎，係割席㗎！（見面）真係會影響心情。」他更笑稱不想被新年情緒勒索，被迫與不想見的親戚碰頭，故今年只會到訪應見、必須見的家人。"},{"pid":"b6306e199644df37fe0505bea9c2c4e56e83a6c9","tid":2406071,"uid":116827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"99a5215423c28fdcd28e5207236f6cd8d2e07d52","tid":2406071,"uid":252972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"如果藍屍親戚唔見仲好"},{"pid":"5b0805e226a74de302fac98574dc6a444a8b50ed","tid":2406071,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"新年d垃圾文化真係可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}